image_analysis.description: A photograph showing the top three shelves of a white built-in bookcase or storage unit. The shelves are filled with white storage boxes and file organizers. The top shelf contains five white vertical file holders with small metal label frames. The middle shelf contains three large white storage boxes with lids and cut-out handles, each with a small printed label. The bottom visible shelf contains several stacked white boxes and two more vertical file holders in the center. The unit is topped with a decorative crown molding.
image_analysis.layout: Three horizontal shelves within a white wooden frame.
